    "name": "Andhra Style Chicken Biriyani",
    "description": "Andhra-style chicken pulao is a flavorful one-pot rice dish made with tender chicken, fragrant basmati rice, and a bold mix of spices. What sets it apart is the generous use of mint and coriander, giving it a fresh, slightly spicy kick without being as heavy as biryani. Perfect for a quick, satisfying meal with rich South Indian flavors.",
